                                        aired on TV Tokyo and Wowow from 1998 to 1999. It was created and animated by
                                        Sunrise, led by a production team of director Shinichirō Watanabe, screenwriter
                                        Keiko Nobumoto, character designer Toshihiro Kawamoto, mechanical designer Kimitoshi
                                        Yamane, and composer Yoko Kanno, who are collectively billed as Hajime Yatate.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4">
                            <img class="w-14" src="/assets/save_icon.png" alt="save-icon">
                            <img class="h-24 md:-rotate-90" src="/assets/arrow-drawn-black.png" alt="arrow">
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center mr-4">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Save in Library</h3>
                            <img class="max-w-[500px]" src="/assets/my_library.png" alt="search_image">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-full mt-4">
                        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-center">Save the articles that you like the most and check them out in your library any time you want.</p>
                    </div>
                </section>


                <section class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center shadow-lg p-6 my-6 rounded-md min-h-[600px]">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row w-full justify-center items-center gap-10">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">From Library</h3>
                            <div class="flex items-center m-8">
